# Environment Variables
#
# Copy this file to .env and fill in the values:
#   cp .env.example .env
#
# Never commit .env to version control. It will be added to .gitignore
# during Phase 4 (Project Skeleton).
#
# Additional variables for infrastructure (database, cache, storage, etc.)
# will be added in Phase 3 once the architecture is confirmed.

# ── npm (package publishing) ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Automation token for publishing to the npm registry via CI/CD.
# Create at: https://www.npmjs.com/settings/<your-username>/tokens
# Store as a GitHub Actions secret named NPM_TOKEN — do not commit the value here.
NPM_TOKEN=

# ── Phase 3 (Architecture) ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Variables for databases, caching, storage, and other infrastructure
# will be added here once the architecture is confirmed.
